headline.print_headline: Vodafone Lodges Complaint Over Telefonica in Spain
headline.main: Vodafone Lodges Complaint Over Telefonica in Spain

lead_paragraph: Vodafone has lodged a complaint against Spanish rival Telefonica, alleging it is abusing its position in Spain to reduce competition for telecoms, Internet and television services.
